                            <comment id="16885043" author="yunta" created="Mon, 15 Jul 2019 10:21:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After digging into the heap dump of jobmanager provided by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=zhuzh&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;zhuzh&quot;&gt;zhuzh&lt;/a&gt;, I figured out the root cause. To be short, this is due to &lt;tt&gt;currentPeriodicTrigger&lt;/tt&gt; in &lt;tt&gt;CheckpointCoordinator&lt;/tt&gt; had been assigned to &lt;tt&gt;null&lt;/tt&gt; during triggering checkpoint as there still existed a pending &lt;tt&gt;checkpoint-387&lt;/tt&gt;. However, the pending checkpoints would then be aborted due to the region failover and no active &lt;tt&gt;currentPeriodicTrigger&lt;/tt&gt; anymore.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16887735" author="srichter" created="Thu, 18 Jul 2019 08:04:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Merged in:&lt;br/&gt;
master: 1ec34249a0&lt;br/&gt;
release-1.9: b7bfafca14&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
